Responsibilities:

  Provide assurance services and be in charge of a portfolio of clients
  Plan, execute and complete the audit of companies
  Develop and maintain cordial working relationship with client personnel
  Ad hoc assignments as assigned

Requirements:

  You should have at least 3 years of audit experience
  Accountancy graduates or ACCA graduates
  Preferably a Chartered Accountant
  Proactive, committed and able to work under pressure
